---
title: Speedy Middle Eastern Inspired Harissa Lamb with Pepper and Bulgur Wheat
description: Ready in just 25 minutes, this Speedy Middle Eastern Inspired Harissa Lamb is quick but full of flavour. Harissa is widely used in Middle Eastern and North African cuisine, containing dried chillies, star anise, cumin and coriander.
